2, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"strategy director\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 144}, {\"ngram\": \"art director\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"creative director\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Background:\\\"The purpose of this campaign was to excite and engage Canadians around Team Canada at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, and we needed to employ athlete-centric storytelling,\\\" says Jean George.\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Background:\\\"The purpose\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"this campaign\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"Canadians\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 286}, {\"ngram\": \"Team Canada\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete-centric storytelling\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"Jean George\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While the target for this campaign could have been all Canadians, we knew we needed to narrow down and better define the audiences we were looking to resonate with, so we focused on casual Olympics viewers and younger Canadians.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"this campaign\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"all Canadians\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"the audiences\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"casual Olympics viewers\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"younger Canadians\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This audience, especially younger Canadians, possessed the most pessimistic outlook of the country and overall had lower levels of Canadian pride than the rest of the population.\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.7836866814419725, \"rank\": 0.25160948878974737, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This audience\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"especially younger Canadians\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 685}, {\"ngram\": \"the most pessimistic outlook\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 725}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"lower levels\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If we could connect with them, we ultimately could increase the relevance of our campaign and increase viewership and overall support of Team Canada at the 2024 Olympics Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relevance\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"our campaign\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"viewership\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"overall support\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"Team Canada\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics Games\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Design thinking:\\\"We knew we had to approach this Olympic campaign differently from a strategy perspective than in years past,\\\" says George.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Design thinking:\\\"We\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic campaign\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"a strategy perspective\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So much has happened within our nation in recent years, so to rely on traditional notions and symbols of Canadian pride to spark excitement for these Olympic Games would have missed the mark.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.7836866814419725, \"rank\": 0.25160948878974737, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our nation\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional notions\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"symbols\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"the mark\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We orchestrated focus groups, took consumer polls and conducted extensive research to get a pulse check on how people were feeling about life in Canada-and where, if at all, the Olympics fit into their view of modern life.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"focus groups\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer polls\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"extensive research\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"a pulse check\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"Canada\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"their view\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"modern life\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What the team found was truly enlightening: Canadians are very driven by achievement, but within our nation's current circumstances, they are not confident they can reach their goals,\\\" George continues.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"Canadians\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"achievement\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"our nation's current circumstances\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"their goals\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While this strategic discovery was somewhat sobering, the notion of obstacles impeding success provided a very clear and powerful point of connection between Canadians and Team Canada Olympic athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this strategic discovery\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"the notion\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"obstacles\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"a very clear and powerful point\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"Canadians\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"Team Canada Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Challenges:\\\"As discussed, we were taking an athlete-centric approach to our storytelling,\\\" say Mike Albrecht and Ryan Speziale.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albrecht_Haushofer\", \"score\": 0.9999999976944309, \"rank\": 2.3053751172912928e-09, \"text\": \"Albrecht\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albrecht_Haushofer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albrecht_Haushofer\"}, {\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\", \"score\": 0.964877494980454, \"rank\": 0.028845830615256102, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\"}, {\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\", \"score\": 0.9999997199879936, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Speziale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Challenges:\\\"As\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete-centric approach\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"our storytelling\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Therefore, our creative needed to have our athletes at the forefront.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While we could not capture the entire team, ensuring we could get a diverse set of athletes coming from different parts of the country was important.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the entire team\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"a diverse set\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"different parts\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2284}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And therein lay the most challenging aspect of the project.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most challenging aspect\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"the project\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We needed to coordinate times to capture content from our chosen athletes during an Olympic year, so we were competing against their rigorous training schedules,\\\" the pair continues.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2425}, {\"ngram\": \"our chosen athletes\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic year\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"their rigorous training schedules\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To accommodate their schedules, we would fly to them and we were given a maximum of three hours to capture the content we needed.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their schedules\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2591}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximum of three hours\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the content\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During this time, we needed to capture running footage, still photography and do an on-the-spot audio session with them talking about their stories of overcoming obstacles.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"running footage\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2745}, {\"ngram\": \"still photography\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2764}, {\"ngram\": \"the-spot\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"their stories\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"obstacles\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's demanding for trained talent, let alone athletes.\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trained talent\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, our chosen athletes rose to the occasion of the production process, which was brilliantly set up by director Hubert Davis and team as they met with each athlete beforehand to learn more about their story.\\\"\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hubert_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.524051792155926e-22, \"text\": \"Hubert Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hubert_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hubert_Davis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our chosen athletes\", \"from\": 2930, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasion\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"the production process\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"team\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"their story\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Favorite details:\\\"We are so proud of the collaboration our internal teams and partners demonstrated throughout all stages of the creative process,\\\" says George.\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Favorite details:\\\"We\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the collaboration\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"our internal teams\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3210}, {\"ngram\": \"partners\", \"from\": 3215, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"all stages\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"the creative process\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The output turned out the way it did through teamwork and transparent communication.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The output\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"teamwork\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3352}, {\"ngram\": \"transparent communication\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In turn, our creative idea was so strong it wasn't hard to convince Michael J.\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"our creative idea\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3410}, {\"ngram\": \"Michael J.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox and Celine Dion to lend their voices to the campaign.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3463, \"end\": 3466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/20th_Century_Studios\", \"score\": 0.5527329147392062, \"rank\": 0.8085956556920295, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/20th_Century_Studios\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/20th_Century_Studios\"}, {\"begin\": 3471, \"end\": 3482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7827443615096645e-34, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their voices\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We could not think of better representatives to deliver the message of our creative platform.\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"better representatives\", \"from\": 3543, \"to\": 3565}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"our creative platform\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lastly, we felt that it would be imperative to deliver the message of our campaign in an unignorable way to younger Canadians,\\\" George continues.\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3682}, {\"ngram\": \"our campaign\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3698}, {\"ngram\": \"an unignorable way\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3720}, {\"ngram\": \"younger Canadians\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3741}, {\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Therefore, we developed posters and designed classroom-based exercises that teachers across the country could employ with their students.\\\"\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3901, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"posters\", \"from\": 3787, \"to\": 3794}, {\"ngram\": \"designed classroom-based exercises\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"teachers\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3847}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"their students\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visual influences:\\\"The use of archival footage was a core conceptual element of our films,\\\" says Ryan Speziale.\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 4014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4000, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\", \"score\": 0.964877494980454, \"rank\": 0.028845830615256102, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Atwood\"}, {\"begin\": 4005, \"end\": 4013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\", \"score\": 0.9999997199879936, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Speziale\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Speziale\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Visual influences:\\\"The use\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"archival footage\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3949}, {\"ngram\": \"a core conceptual element\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"our films\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We wanted to really contrast the way we typically see our Team Canada athletes by using existing broadcast footage, then mixing those shots with more emotive and introspective moments that peek behind the scenes.\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our Team Canada\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4085}, {\"ngram\": \"existing broadcast footage\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4130}, {\"ngram\": \"those shots\", \"from\": 4144, \"to\": 4155}, {\"ngram\": \"more emotive and introspective moments\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4199}, {\"ngram\": \"the scenes\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From a design perspective, we wanted to project that bravery is a state of being and is an ever-evolving reaction,\\\" Speziale continues.\", \"from\": 4230, \"to\": 4366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a design perspective\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4256}, {\"ngram\": \"that bravery\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4291}, {\"ngram\": \"a state\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4302}, {\"ngram\": \"an ever-evolving reaction\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"Speziale\", \"from\": 4347, \"to\": 4355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And we felt the use of white and red aura could create an organic, free-flowing excitement of bravery and would best embody the unbeatable mindset of Canadian athletes.\", \"from\": 4367, \"to\": 4536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4518, \"end\": 4526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"score\": 0.7836866814419725, \"rank\": 0.25160948878974737, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"white and red aura\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4409}, {\"ngram\": \"an organic, free-flowing excitement\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"bravery\", \"from\": 4462, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"the unbeatable mindset\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In static executions, we employed a gradi